    "description":  "How to buy MOT slots so your business can record MOT test results, including managing your account and getting refunds.",
    "details":  {
                    "attachments":  [
                                        {
                                            "accessible":  false,
                                            "alternative_format_contact_email":  "accessible-formats@dvsa-publishing.zendesk.com",
                                            "attachment_type":  "file",
