                                            "id":  "7682096",
                                            "number_of_pages":  1,
                                            "title":  "application to pay for MOT slots by cheque or postal order",
                                            "url":  "https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/65ba3a0fee7d49000d984a49/mot-slot-payment-by-cheque-or-postal-order.pdf"
                                        }
                                    ],
                    "body":  "\u003cdiv class=\"govspeak\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eYou have to pay the Driver and Vehicle Standards Agency (DVSA) for each passed MOT test your business records on the MOT testing service.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eYou do this by buying MOT test slots in advance. You use one slot for each pass that’s recorded.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe slots can be used by any MOT centre in your business.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"who-can-buy-mot-slots\"\u003eWho can buy MOT slots\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eTo buy slots, you need to be either the:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eauthorised examiner designated manager (AEDM) – the person who oversees the management, operation and quality of all MOTs in the business\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eauthorised examiner delegate (AED) – a person who helps the AEDM with managing MOT testing\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"buy-mot-slots\"\u003eBuy MOT slots\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eYou can:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eset up a Direct Debit to buy a set amount of slots each month (you can change the amount if you need to)\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003ebuy slots as and when you need them by debit card, credit card, cheque or postal order\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eYou can buy 25 to 125,000 slots per transaction.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eEach slot costs £2.05. VAT is not charged on MOT slots.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch3 id=\"set-up-a-direct-debit\"\u003eSet up a Direct Debit\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eYou can set up a Direct Debit to automatically buy a set amount of slots each month. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eYou can choose for the payment to be taken on the 5th or 20th day of each month.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv role=\"note\" aria-label=\"Information\" class=\"application-notice info-notice\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eYou must be authorised to set up a Direct Debit on the account you want to use. Contact your bank if you’re not sure you are authorised to set up a Direct Debit from your bank account.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003col class=\"steps\"\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSign in to the \u003ca href=\"https://www.gov.uk/mot-testing-service\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eMOT testing service\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSelect your business name, for example ‘John Smith Motors Ltd’.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSelect \u003cstrong\u003eSet up Direct Debit\u003c/strong\u003e under the \u003cstrong\u003eBuy slots\u003c/strong\u003e button.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFollow the instructions to set up your Direct Debit.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ol\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eIt can take up to 5 working days for the new slots to be added to your account when you pay by Direct Debit.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch4 id=\"change-how-many-slots-you-buy\"\u003eChange how many slots you buy\u003c/h4\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eYou can change the amount of slots you buy by Direct Debit in the MOT testing service. You need to change the amount at least 10 working days before your next monthly payment is due.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch3 id=\"pay-by-debit-or-credit-card\"\u003ePay by debit or credit card\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003col class=\"steps\"\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSign in to the \u003ca href=\"https://www.gov.uk/mot-testing-service\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eMOT testing service\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSelect your business name, for example, ‘John Smith Motors Ltd’.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSelect the \u003cstrong\u003eBuy slots\u003c/strong\u003e button.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eFollow the instructions to buy slots with a debit or credit card.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ol\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eIt can take up to 30 minutes for the new slots to be added to your account when you pay by debit or credit card.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch3 id=\"pay-by-cheque-or-postal-order\"\u003ePay by cheque or postal order\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eYou can pay by cheque or postal order if you cannot pay by card or Direct Debit.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eDownload, fill in and print the \u003cspan class=\"gem-c-attachment-link\"\u003e\n  \u003ca class=\"govuk-link\" href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/65ba3a0fee7d49000d984a49/mot-slot-payment-by-cheque-or-postal-order.pdf\"\u003eapplication to pay for MOT slots by cheque or postal order\u003c/a\u003e  (\u003cspan class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\"\u003e\u003cabbr title=\"Portable Document Format\" class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__abbr\"\u003ePDF\u003c/abbr\u003e\u003c/span\u003e, \u003cspan class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\"\u003e175 KB\u003c/span\u003e, \u003cspan class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\"\u003e1 page\u003c/span\u003e)\u003c/span\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eSend the form with a cheque or postal order made payable to DVSA.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv class=\"address\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"adr org fn\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\n\nCash Management Team  \n\u003cbr\u003eDVSA  \n\u003cbr\u003eThe Ellipse  \n\u003cbr\u003ePadley Road  \n\u003cbr\u003eSwansea  \n\u003cbr\u003eSA1 8AN\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"monitor-your-mot-slot-usage\"\u003eMonitor your MOT slot usage\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eWhen you sign in to the MOT testing service you can:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003esee your overall slot balance across your MOT testing business\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003esee your transaction history – how many slots you have bought and which payment method you used\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003emonitor how many slots each MOT centre has used\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"get-a-refund\"\u003eGet a refund\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eYou can apply for a refund and to reduce your MOT slot balance if:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eyou’ve bought too many MOT slots\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eyour balance is too high\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv role=\"note\" aria-label=\"Information\" class=\"application-notice info-notice\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThere’s a different process to get a refund if you’re \u003ca href=\"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/close-your-mot-centre\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eclosing an MOT centre\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eYou’ll need your MOT testing business’ authorisation number (called an Authorised Examiner ID).\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv class=\"call-to-action\"\u003e\n  \u003cp\u003e\u003ca rel=\"external\" href=\"https://submit.forms.service.gov.uk/form/920/apply-for-a-refund-of-mot-slot-payments/\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eApply for a refund and to reduce your MOT slot balance\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003ch3 id=\"what-happens-next\"\u003eWhat happens next\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eIf you paid by:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003edebit or credit card, you’ll get a refund to the card within 5 working days\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eDirect Debit, you’ll get a refund by cheque within 14 working days\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003echeque or postal order, you’ll get a refund by cheque within 14 working days\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"get-help-buying-slots\"\u003eGet help buying slots\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eContact the MOT testing service desk to get help buying MOT slots or getting a refund.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv class=\"contact\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMOT testing service desk \u003cbr\u003e\nTelephone: 0330 123 5654 \u003cbr\u003e\nMonday to Friday, 8am to 6pm (excluding public holidays)\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ca href=\"https://www.gov.uk/call-charges\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eFind out about call charges\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e",
